WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.130 --> 00:00:04.460
HipChat is a system for
chatting with other OMS students live.

00:00:04.460 --> 00:00:09.230
To sign up, first go to hipchat.com and
then click to sign up.

00:00:09.230 --> 00:00:12.180
Then click Join an existing team.

00:00:12.180 --> 00:00:15.220
Enter your name and
Georgia Tech address.

00:00:15.220 --> 00:00:19.840
Then in this field, type gotech-omscs

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:24.020
then click Continue,
then wait to be accepted.

00:00:24.020 --> 00:00:28.110
Once you're accepted,
return to hipchat.com and then log in,

00:00:28.110 --> 00:00:31.450
then you'll see the screen.

00:00:31.450 --> 00:00:33.370
Let's take a look at the web app.

00:00:33.370 --> 00:00:37.178
&gt;From there, you can start chatting
with your classmates in the rooms or

00:00:37.178 --> 00:00:37.866
one on one.

